{"TopicId":131838,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Fuel Flow on planes","CreatedByName":"Dfthu","CreatedById":80296,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T04:14:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dfthu","CreatedById":80296,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T04:14:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a SSTO that i\u0027m making and its pulling fuel from all of the thanks. I want it to flow like in the picture below\u00A0and keep to the rocket fuel tanks full.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Hr7mLte.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Hr7mLte.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-11T04:14:52Z\u0022 title=\u002202/11/2016 04:14  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 11, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Dfthu\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Val","CreatedById":126227,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T11:27:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can\u0027t change how the Jets/RAPIERs drain fuel without editing config files, but you can control their fuel flow with parts that have (tweakable) fuel crossfeed, like decouplers and docking ports.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy preferred parts for use with spaceplanes are:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ctable style=\u0022font-size:14px;margin:1em 0px;border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);border-collapse:collapse;color:#000000;font-family:sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(249,249,249);\u0022\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022width:61px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/File:Small_hardpoint.png\u0022 style=\u0022text-decoration:none;color:rgb(11,0,128);margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;background:none;\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Small hardpoint.png\u0022 height=\u002260\u0022 src=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/images/thumb/5/5c/Small_hardpoint.png/17px-Small_hardpoint.png\u0022 srcset=\u0022/images/thumb/5/5c/Small_hardpoint.png/26px-Small_hardpoint.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5c/Small_hardpoint.png/34px-Small_hardpoint.png 2x\u0022 style=\u0022border:none;vertical-align:middle;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Small_Hardpoint\u0022 style=\u0022text-decoration:none;color:rgb(11,0,128);background:none;\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESmall Hardpoint\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\nRadial mounted\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E60\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E0.05\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E2\u2009000\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n20\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E600\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022width:61px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/File:Structural_Pylon.png\u0022 style=\u0022text-decoration:none;color:rgb(11,0,128);margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;background:none;\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Structural Pylon.png\u0022 height=\u002260\u0022 src=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/images/thumb/0/0e/Structural_Pylon.png/17px-Structural_Pylon.png\u0022 srcset=\u0022/images/thumb/0/0e/Structural_Pylon.png/25px-Structural_Pylon.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0e/Structural_Pylon.png/34px-Structural_Pylon.png 2x\u0022 style=\u0022border:none;vertical-align:middle;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Structural_Pylon\u0022 style=\u0022text-decoration:none;color:rgb(11,0,128);background:none;\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EStructural Pylon\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\nRadial mounted\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E125\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E0.2\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E2\u2009000\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n70\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:1px solid rgb(170,170,170);padding:.2em;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E2\u2009500\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can offset them into the fuel tanks if you don\u0027t want them visible, disable their staging in their right click menu, and if needed put their crossfeed toggle in the same action group you use to switch the RAPIER mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt will approximate what you want, but it\u0027s not quite the same.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}